{"word":"πολυπλανής","slug":"πολυπλανής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πολυπλανής</b></el> <el>(πολυ-πλᾰνής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>πλανάομαι</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>roaming far</i> or <i>long</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>π. κισσός</el> the <i>straying</i> ivy, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>much-erring</i>, or, <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>leading much astray</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}